      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"letting the pieces rest\"... that's what you're saying? that it's okay to just stop trying to fight it? because it feels like every time i try to \"heal\" or \"get better\" it's just exhausting and pointless. like im just fighting against gravity at this point.",
