      "content": "a quiet surrender... that actually sounds kind of beautiful. peaceful, almost. but it's also kind of scary to think about. like, if i actually stop fighting and just let the weight settle, there's no going back, right? it's like once you stop trying to hold it all together, everything just finally ends.",
